<p>The <code>border</code> property matches the first OR last iteration.</p>

<pre>{open}users{close}
  {open}property:border{close}*{open}/property:border{close}{open}$name{close}&lt;br&gt;
{open}/users{close}</pre>

<h3>Result:</h3>
{users}
  {property:border}*{/property:border}{$name}<br>
{/users}
